data.name: Jarver's Crypt
data.text: I found my first group project relatively easily technically. What I hadn't anticipated was the challenges of working in a team of people who all had their own strengths and weaknesses. I learnt very quickly that soft skills are just as, if not more important as technical skills. Guiding my teammates through the problems we encountered, without taking control, became my goal throughout the project, with a long term goal of refining the qualities of a good servant leader.
